STATE of North Carolina
v.
James Albert COLEY, Jr. No. 399P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 16, 2006. James Albert Coley, Jr., Pro Se. Kathleen U. Baldwin, Assistant Attorney General, Roxann Vaneekhoven, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 31st day of July 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th day of November 2006."
